'''ᱨᱟᱣᱤᱱᱟ ᱫᱮᱥᱨᱟᱡᱽ''' ({{lang-ne|रवीना देशराज श्रेष्ठ}}) ᱢᱤᱫᱴᱟᱝ ᱱᱮᱯᱟᱞ ᱨᱮᱱ ᱢᱤᱰᱤᱭᱟ ᱟᱨ ᱱᱤᱡᱮ ᱵᱮᱸᱠᱟᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ᱾ ᱢᱮᱜᱟ ᱵᱮᱸᱠ ᱨᱮᱱ ᱢᱤᱫ (ᱰᱮᱯᱩᱴᱭ ᱪᱦᱤᱮᱝ ᱮᱽᱮᱪᱩᱴᱤᱶᱮ ᱚᱝᱝᱤᱪᱮᱨ ) ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱾ ᱥᱨᱮᱴᱷ ᱫᱚ ᱟᱹᱰᱤᱜᱟᱱ ᱡᱮᱜᱮᱛ ᱟᱨ<ref>{{cite web|url=https://famousnepali.com/people/raveena-desraj-shrestha-joshi/|title=Raveena details|publisher=famousnepali}}</ref> ᱡᱮᱡᱮᱜᱮᱛᱟᱹᱨᱤ ᱠᱚᱨᱮ ᱥᱤᱨᱯᱷᱟᱹ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱢᱟᱹᱱ ᱦᱟᱢᱮᱴ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱭᱟ ᱟᱨ ᱱᱮᱯᱟᱞ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱵᱮᱸᱠ/ᱤᱱᱴᱚᱨᱴᱮᱱᱢᱮᱱᱴ ᱥᱮᱪᱴᱚᱨ ᱠᱚᱨᱮ ᱩᱱᱤ ᱫᱚ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢᱟᱱ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱦᱩᱭᱩᱜ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ᱾ᱥᱨᱮᱥᱴᱷ ᱫᱚ ᱢᱤᱫ (ᱝᱸᱪᱪᱤ) ᱦᱚᱛᱮᱛᱮ ᱣᱚᱢᱣᱮᱱ ᱤᱱᱴᱟᱨᱯᱨᱮᱱᱚᱨ ᱰᱮᱣᱞᱚᱯᱢᱮᱱᱴ ᱠᱚᱢᱤᱴᱤ ᱨᱮᱱ ᱣᱚᱭᱤᱥ ᱪᱮᱭᱨᱢᱟᱱ ᱵᱟᱪᱷᱱᱟᱣ ᱟᱠᱟᱱ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱭᱟ ᱟᱨ ᱒᱐᱑᱘ ᱨᱮ ᱱᱮᱯᱟᱞ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱱᱟᱜᱟᱢ ᱨᱮ ᱥᱚᱨᱮᱥ ᱛᱤᱨᱞᱟᱹ ᱞᱮᱠᱟᱛᱮ ᱛᱟᱞᱠᱟ ᱨᱮ ᱥᱮᱞᱮᱫ ᱮ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ᱾<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thehimalayantimes.com/business/samsung-galaxy-s7-edge-s7-nepal/|title=Samsung Galaxy S7 and S7 Edge in Nepal|publisher=thehimalayantimes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://kathmandupost.ekantipur.com/printedition/news/2013-08-03/crowning-glory.html|title=Crowning glory|publisher=kathmandupost}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://lexlimbu.com/blog/2019/06/26/priyanka-karki-shrinkhala-khatiwada-raveena-desraj-join-namaste-eid-2019/|title=Namaste Eid 2019|publisher=Lexlimbu}}</ref> coaching,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thehimalayantimes.com/lifestyle/automobile/yamaha-miss-nepal-take-road-safety/|title= Yamaha and Miss Nepal take on road safety|publisher=thehimalayantimes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.standupforpassion.com/events-main/2016/9/27/nov-17-2016-kathmandu-nepal|title=Stand up for passion event|publisher=standupforpassion}}</ref> etc.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://daughtersofthehimalayas.wordpress.com/2015/03/02/spotlight-on-leading-women-of-nepal-raveena-desraj-shrestha/|title=Leading Women of Nepal – Raveena Desraj Shrestha|publisher=daughtersofthehimalayas}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://living.com.np/tech/techie-at-the-core|title=Techie at the core|publisher=living}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://wowmagnepal.com/is-social-media-stealing-your-life/|title=Is social media stealing your life?|publisher=wow